My name is Matthew Reyes (he/him/his).

I spend my free time with my dog, Bisbee, and getting outdoors to climb rocks or bike around.

title: Matthew Reyes
text:
My name is Matthew Reyes (he/him/his), and I am based in Oakland, CA.
I’m an aspiring data science and public health professional, having recently completed a Master’s in Public Health focusing in epidemiology and biostatistics. I’ve worked on health disparity research for patients with rare lung diseases, UX research and design for an open-source mobile health application, and performed equity analysis for digital health products at UCSF.
In my free time, I enjoy a variety of activities, which lately include:

rock climbing
watercolors
practicing spanish and salsa dancing.

I also have a dog named Bisbee who occupies most of my time and attention:
